<p>"<b>Southern Nights</b>" is a song written by <a href="Allen_Toussaint" title="Allen Toussaint">Allen Toussaint</a> and most famously recorded by <a href="United_States" title="United States">American</a> <a href="Country_music" title="Country music">country music</a> singer, <a href="Glen_Campbell" title="Glen Campbell">Glen Campbell</a>. It was the first single released from Campbell's 1977 album, <i><a href="Southern_Nights_(Glen_Campbell_album)" title="Southern Nights (Glen Campbell album)">Southern Nights</a></i>, and reached #1 on various country and <a href="Pop_music" title="Pop music">pop</a> charts.</p>
