<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Southern_Nights_(song)&action=edit&section=5.php.html" title="Edit section: Awards">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Awards">Awards</span></h2>
<p>"Southern Nights" was certified gold in the United States for sales of 1 million units by the <a href="Recording_Industry_Association_of_America" title="Recording Industry Association of America">Recording Industry Association of America</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external autonumber" href="http://www.riaa.com/gp/database/search_results.asp">[3]</a> In 1977, the song was nominated for <a href="Country_Music_Association_Awards" title="Country Music Association Awards">Song of the Year</a> by the <a href="Country_Music_Association" title="Country Music Association">Country Music Association</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-5" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-5"><span>[</span>5<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
